### Air Quality - Create record
POST http://localhost:3000/api/air-quality
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "station_name": "Station 1",
  "city_name": "Kyiv",
  "pm25": 25.3,
  "pm10": 35.2,
  "no2": 15.5,
  "measurement_time": "2025-11-26"
}

###
### Air Quality - Get all records
GET http://localhost:3000/api/air-quality

###
### Air Quality - Get record by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/air-quality/{id}

###
### Air Quality - Update record
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/air-quality/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pm25": 30.5,
  "no2": 20.1
}

###
### Air Quality - Delete record
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/air-quality/{id}

